description: This little trailer is bringing big flavors to the streets of Tampa with their fresh and made-to-order selection of breakfast, burgers, and more!A few of the tasty items they’re slinging include…Kim’s Spinach Feta Wrap- delicious spinach, mushrooms, and onions with two Circle 6 farm fresh eggs and feta cheese wrapped in a flour tortillaReuben Burger- 1/4 lb handmade all-beef patty topped with tender and perfectly seasoned corned beef, swiss cheese, and sauerkraut with thousand island dressing on a toasted kaiser rollVegan Smoky Black Bean Chili- a medium chili with a nice chipotle-smoked flavor with cheese and/or chopped onionFor all this and further deliciousness, invite Fork in the Road Mobile Eatery to make its way to your next event!
name: Fork In The Road Mobile Eatery
